Adeniyi Olugbemi, Sokoto Four customers of Fidelity Bank in Sokoto State have won mouth-watering cash rewards for their loyalty to the bank in the ongoing Fidelity Reward Savings Account promo. The trio of Bashar Maccido, Gummi Ibrahim and Muriba Global Ventures Limited were rewarded with N500,000 each, while Ikeuno Gloria Nkemjika, won N150,000 in the Children Sweeter Account for below 18 years old customers. The bank’s Regional Head, Salihu Jubril, at the presentation held at the Nigerian Automobile Technicians Association secretariat, stated, “The reward is real because at Fidelity Bank, we keep our word. “Another draw will hold in a fortnight for fifty depositors. All eligible customers need to do is to open an account, with a minimum of N20,000 in their account and qualify for the next draw.” Bashar Maccido, who spoke on behalf of the beneficiaries, expressed excitement over the reward and encouraged others to open account with the bank and benefit in the reward. Copyright PUNCH.
